Introduction

Kaylee is a Korean-American singer under JYP Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group VCHA formed by the survival show "A2K" under JYP Entertainment. She debuted in VCHA on January 26, 2024, with their first single album 'Girls of the Year".

Before their first comeback on March 15, 2024, JYP Entertainment announced that she was to take an indefinite hiatus due to medical concerns.
